# 📝 Problem Statement

Direction Sense questions test our ability to determine the final direction, distance and position after movements.

---

# 🧭 Basic Directions

```text
            North
              ↑

West    ←     ●     → East

              ↓
            South
```

---

# 💡 Concepts

### Right Turn

```text
North → East

East → South

South → West

West → North
```

### Left Turn

```text
North → West

West → South

South → East

East → North
```

---

# 🧠 Memory Trick

```text
RIGHT TURN

N → E

E → S

S → W

W → N

-----------------

LEFT TURN

N → W

W → S

S → E

E → N
```

---

# 📌 Important Rules

### Four Right Turns

```text
Same Direction
```

### Four Left Turns

```text
Same Direction
```

### Two Right Turns

```text
Opposite Direction
```

### Two Left Turns

```text
Opposite Direction
```

---

# 🔍 Example 1

A person faces North.

Turns right.

Direction?

Answer

```text
East
```

---

# 🔍 Example 2

A person faces South.

Turns left.

Direction?

Answer

```text
East
```

---

# 🔍 Example 3

A person faces West.

Turns right.

Turns left.

Turns left.

Direction?

Answer

```text
South
```

